Name: HangOutGame
About the game: HangOutGame is a game about climbing. Sometimes it may be difficult because of different obstacles. You can use a rope with hook, a blaster and your agility. Your task is getting to the finish in each world. You can do it by yourself or unite with a friend. Good luck! Also players can create their own worlds!
